God Almighty, His Honour shall be rescued unhurt, and the bandits brought to book, Amen.  “Let us keep His Honour in our prayers, please,” the statement added.   The Police Public Relations Officer, DSP Chidi Nwabuzor when contacted said he was yet to get the details of the incident.  MEN of the Delta State police command have arrested a kidnap gang that abducted a female magistrate in the state, just as the command also rescued another kidnap victim in Edo State. In "News" By Gabriel Enogholase LEADERS of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) have stunned voters in Igueben Local Government Area of the State with the achievements of its party Candidate for the September 19, 2020 Governorship election in Edo State, Governor Godwin Obaseki in the past four years in Edo Senatorial district… In "Edo Decides" By Alemma-Ozioruva Aliu, Benin city The Edo State Command of the Nigerian Security and Civil Defence Corps (NSCDC) has deployed its personnel around the forests in Igueben area of Edo State where two its men were on Friday afternoon kidnapped by suspected kidnappers.   Public Relations Officer of NSCDC state… In "News"